snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythm Festival — Announcement Trailer - Arriving on New Platforms!
snippet.description:
#TaikonoTatsujin: Rhythm Festival ​
Will be available on PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, Windows PC and Steam® on 7 November!✨

For the first time in a home-release, the game supports 120 FPS! Look forward to new platform-exclusive collaborative songs and mini characters.🎵​

Click here for more details: https://bnent.asia/TnTRF-Port
